206
00:13:33,980 --> 00:13:36,830
My supplier is the drug lord Kyaw Myint Tun.

207
00:13:37,070 --> 00:13:38,850
His nickname is Duya Tiger.

208
00:13:39,060 --> 00:13:40,850
