209
00:13:40,910 --> 00:13:42,030
into the country from Nangui.

210
00:13:42,050 --> 00:13:44,170
Then there are people who rent cars to transport them to Mincheng,

211
00:13:44,370 --> 00:13:46,190
where they're handed over to a person called Madam Xue.

212
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:49,030
