213
00:13:49,040 --> 00:13:50,930
further sort and package these drugs.

214
00:13:51,390 --> 00:13:53,000
Then they're delivered to Zhao Wenbin.

215
00:13:53,940 --> 00:13:56,380
Bai Xiaohui, Fan Lingling,

216
00:13:56,650 --> 00:13:57,770
Qiu Hailong,

217
00:13:58,030 --> 00:13:59,440
Zhang Yong, and Feng Tianyi.

218
00:14:00,130 --> 00:14:02,140
Was it you who ordered Wang Xuehua to kill them?

219
00:14:03,150 --> 00:14:04,330
Yes, it was me.

220
00:14:04,710 --> 00:14:06,380
Bai Xiaohui

221
00:14:06,800 --> 00:14:08,870
