223
00:14:11,620 --> 00:14:13,110
We had no choice but to kill her.

224
00:14:13,150 --> 00:14:14,570
Where were Bai Xiaohui and Fan Lingling

225
00:14:14,580 --> 00:14:15,740
killed?

226
00:14:15,950 --> 00:14:17,910
How were the bodies transported?

227
00:14:17,940 --> 00:14:19,560
They both happened in the basement

228
00:14:19,670 --> 00:14:21,360
of Wang Xuehua's hardware store.

229
00:14:22,580 --> 00:14:24,820
Bai Xiaohui's case was special.

230
00:14:24,980 --> 00:14:26,750
That day, we noticed that all your people

231
00:14:26,790 --> 00:14:28,130
were in Limin Lane.

232
00:14:28,160 --> 00:14:29,370
So Wang Xuehua and I

233
00:14:29,470 --> 00:14:31,980
had to dismember her body,

234
00:14:32,100 --> 00:14:34,440
put it in sealed bags, and vacuum seal them.

235
00:14:35,070 --> 00:14:37,200
The next day, we mixed the bags into a box of tea leaves

236
00:14:37,270 --> 00:14:38,270
and transported them out.

237
00:14:38,660 --> 00:14:40,650
When we were transporting the body that day,

238
00:14:41,390 --> 00:14:42,640
Han Qing happened to come to see me.

239
00:14:42,880 --> 00:14:45,760
She also helped me move the box containing the body.

240
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:47,730
