255
00:15:30,230 --> 00:15:31,920
on the mountain in the forest park.

256
00:15:32,110 --> 00:15:34,380
He said he wanted Zhong Wei to be closer to home.

257
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:38,320
What's the deal with Zhong Wei's hair and Fan Lingling's blood stains

258
00:15:38,430 --> 00:15:40,590
found in Unit A1, Limin Lane?

259
00:15:41,280 --> 00:15:44,440
I had Wang Xuehua keep them.

260
00:15:58,060 --> 00:15:59,620
I originally planned to

261
00:15:59,660 --> 00:16:00,620
pin the murders

262
00:16:00,620 --> 00:16:02,630
on Zhao Wenbin later,

263
00:16:03,430 --> 00:16:05,160
because Zhao Wenbin was unreliable.

264
00:16:05,900 --> 00:16:08,980
I was worried he might turn on us one day.

265
00:16:10,990 --> 00:16:13,660
I didn't expect the incident with Bai Xiaohui to happen.

266
00:16:13,910 --> 00:16:16,280
So I had to use it on Zhong Wei instead.

267
00:16:17,810 --> 00:16:19,540
Zhong Wei was really pitiful.

268
00:16:19,910 --> 00:16:21,340
He was in love with my sister.

269
00:16:21,510 --> 00:16:22,590
I knew that too.

270
00:16:23,350 --> 00:16:24,580
It's exactly because of this

271
00:16:25,310 --> 00:16:26,840
that I had to kill Zhong Wei.

272
00:16:28,510 --> 00:16:29,830
Because I think only in this way

273
00:16:30,940 --> 00:16:32,490
