274
00:16:32,880 --> 00:16:34,760
truly understand that kind of pain.

275
00:16:40,660 --> 00:16:42,340
The pain of having your family taken away,

276
00:16:44,930 --> 00:16:46,490
of losing your loved ones,

277
00:16:48,470 --> 00:16:50,080
and of losing

278
00:16:50,210 --> 00:16:51,230
an ordinary,

279
00:16:52,300 --> 00:16:53,150
humble,

280
00:16:53,980 --> 00:16:56,560
but once peaceful life.

281
00:17:05,810 --> 00:17:07,390
I think Han Qing

282
00:17:10,030 --> 00:17:11,630
should be able to understand that feeling now.

283
